name: UI Balanjaa
description:
Balanjaa is one of the online marketplaces under the auspices of CV. Abisatya Putra Perkasa comes from Cikarang, Kab. Bekasi, West Java, which provides a means of buying and selling from market traders to consumers. All market traders and farmers can provide their best quality merchandise through balances to distribute their products to the wider community for single or multiple transactions.


Thank you,

Rio
